{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a8bdaa08f0","title":"七绝·观潮","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84e2d64f6a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"a8bdaa08f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"3a6a3cc0ab","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"观潮，指观赏浙江省钱塘江口的涌潮。钱塘潮以每年阴历八月十八在海宁所见最为壮观。毛泽东在1957年9月11日（即阴历八月十八），曾乘车去海宁七星庙观潮。"},{"id":"d52160f914","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"钓鱼台，即钓台，在钱塘江中段的富春江边，相传为东汉严光（子陵）隐居垂钓处。"},{"id":"fa5d7eacbd","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"铁马，配有铁甲的战马，借喻雄师劲旅。陆游《十一月四日风雨大作》：“夜闹卧听风吹雨，铁马冰河入梦来。”钱塘江涌潮袭来时，波涛池涌，如闻“十万军声”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"05f5063f20","type":"title","text":"七绝·观潮","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0"},{"id":"3a6a3cc0ab","type":"paragraph","text":"千里波涛滚滚来，雪花飞向钓鱼台回人山纷赞阵容阔，铁马以从容杀敌回。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0"}],"page":{"id":"4e9ac40df0","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a8bdaa08f0","start":236,"end":236}}}},"__N_SSG":true}